},
"128": {
&"character": "Jessica",
&"id": "128",
&"next_id": "129",
&"text": "A dorm wife is a sacred binding between a frat member and a hand picked sorority slut",
&"type": "dialogue"
},
"129": {
&"character": "Jessica",
&"id": "129",
&"next_id": "130",
&"text": "When the time is right, a proven frat member can select a one of the club girls to take for their...",
