raw_text = "~ start
do Story.set_location(\"mabels_room\")
Erika: Well hellooo there new recruits 💋
Erika: Pleased to see a new batch of boys are interested in the frat 🥰
Nina: Knock it off, they're here to worship us
Nina: Stop making'em think they're special
Erika: But they are special 🥰
Erika: Afterall, maybe I'll be lucky enough to be a dorm bride 🥰
Nina: Don't you have a boyfriend or someshit?
Erika: We both know that term doesn't mean anything under Jessica
Erika: Only the dorm brides are special 😘
Nina: Ugh, that old tradition has to die
- [...]
Valerie: Wow, it's so cool to be up here with you girls 😍
Erika: Hi my lovely 🥰
Valerie: Erika 😍
Valerie: Its my first time getting to see the new boys 🤭
Valerie: Let's see who we have 🤩
if Story.has_flag(\"NinasPanties\"):
	Erika: Well well well, I hear one of you got in through Nina
	Player: 👋
	Erika: So you're it huh?
	Erika: I knew she'd fall in love one day 🥰
	Nina: Shut up slut
	Nina: I only let him in to watch him suffer 😒
	Valerie: Wow, he must be special then
	Nina: Ugh for the love of fuck, not you too
	Erika: Tell us dear
	Erika: Are you and Nina lovers yet? 😘
	- No
		Player: No
		Nina: Why would you even ask him that stupid question when I already told you a hundred times?
		Erika: You telling me you aren't keeping any secrets from us? 🤭
		Nina: Why would I keep this like this a secret?
		Nina: Besides he probably has a tiny dick, I don't even give a fuck
		Erika: You don't know that yet 😉
	- Not yet
		Player: Not yet
		Nina: img: nina/15
		Nina: Fuck you mean not yet
		Erika: It means what it means babe
		Erika: This boy is serious about being all tied up with you 🤭
		Erika: I think it would do you a lot of good hehe
		Erika: Hopefully you can fix Nina dear boy 🥰
		Erika: And I'm rooting for you lovers
	Nina: 🙄
	Nina: Maybe I'll just slam my head against a wall for an hour
Valerie: Jason is here 🥰
Jason: Hi Val, brought my friend with me 😉
Valerie: Hiii nice to meet you Jason's friend 🥳🥰
Valerie: img: valerie/8
Valerie: I'm Valerie, but you can call me Val
Player: Hi Val
Valerie: Jason tell meee
Valerie: Is he big like you 🥰
Jason: You'll have to ask him yourself
- I have a girlfriend
	Player: I have a girlfriend
	Valerie: Y-you have a girlfriend?
	Nina: Oh brother, you shouldn't have said that
	Erika: Hehe
	Valerie: 😳😳😳
	Valerie: OMGGGGGGG
	Valerie: I loooove boys that have girlfriends 😭🤎🤎
	Valerie: Maybe I can convince you?
	Valerie: img: valerie/1
	Nina: 🤮
	Valerie: Can I have him all to myself Jess?? PLEAAASE
	Valerie: I want him all for me me me 🥰
	Erika: Jess is gonna be here shortly 🤭
	Nina: Jeez, someone's in heat
- You'll have to find out
	Player: You'll have to find out
	Valerie: Omg he dooooes 😍
	Jason: Of course, all my buds got huge ones
	Player: Jason 😂
	Jason: 🤪
Valerie: Jeez, I suck at this patience thing 😫
Valerie: Hehe 😇
Erika: Well now that everyone's introducing themselves
Erika: I'm Erika and it's a pleasure to meet you all
Erika: 😉💛
Erika: Oh my, we also have Alex finally join the batch too
Erika: And I'm already... familiar with Jason
Erika: That leaves the new boy ☺️
Erika: img: erika/10
Erika: Tell me new boy, do I look good or what?
- Yeah!
	Player: Yeah!
	Erika: 🥰
- Like a goddess 😍
	Player: Like a goddess
	Erika: No need to try to get on my good side
	Erika: You already are 😘
Nina: Alex huh?
Nina: Hello tall dark and handsome
Alex: Yeah, finally in this bitch 😤
Alex: Sup ladies
Alex: img: alex/1
- [...]
Nina: Gym boy huh? 😏
Nina: A cut above the other two dweebs
Jessica: I see everyone's been thoroughly introducing themselves
Jessica: A friendly word of advice to you new boys
Jessica: The girls here might all be forward but don't get any ideas
Jessica: img: jessica/1
- [...]
Jessica: I am the queen of the sorority and my word is law
Jessica: And these girls are here to make sure you follow that law at all times
Jessica: They might even allow you to have a good time
Jessica: Can I get a \"Yes ma'am\"?
Jason: Yes ma'am
Player: Yes ma'am
Alex: Yes queen
Jessica: Good boys
Jessica: You will be given the full benefits of the frat like the grant
Jessica: And if we're really happy with your progress, you can even pick out a dorm wife from the sorority
Jessica: Any questions?
Jason: Oh sweet 🤑
- What's the grant exactly?
	Player: What's the grant exactly?
	Jessica: The club will distribute 2 💵 every week
	Jessica: It should happen every Monday when club check-in occurs
	Jason: Not too shabby
- What's a dorm wife?
	Player: What's a dorm wife?
	Player: It was mentioned before too
	Jessica: I'm glad you asked
	Jessica: A dorm wife is a sacred binding between a frat member and a hand picked sorority slut
	Jessica: When the time is right, a proven frat member can select a one of the club girls to take for their...
	Jessica: Lets say \"personal\" use. The slut will move into her new man's room and become his personal bitch for the rest of her college years
	Jason: Can they refuse? 🤔
	Alex: Who'd wanna refuse me?
	Jessica: If she does refuse however, she is removed from the club for breaking sorority law simply
	Jessica: We've had one such case of this recently but rest assured that it's exceptionally rare for a girl to not comply
	Jessica: We will do everything in our capacity to make sure it is a smooth transition
- Are you available too?
	Player: Are you available too?
	Jessica: What a bold one you are
	if Story.has_flag(\"NinasPanties\")
		Jessica: I heard you took up an invite through Nina
		Jessica: Quite a special feat already
		Nina: Oh brother am I starting to regret that 🙄
		Jessica: But not nearly special enough to be able to grab the queen
	Jessica: You'd need to prove to me that you are eligible
	Jessica: So give it your all okay? 😘
	Jason: Was not expecting that answer 😁
	Jessica: You think as queen, I'd be some sort of heartless monster?
	Jessica: If I can make a committed member out of him, I'll get what I want and a slim chance he might as well 😉
	Jason: Makes sense
Jessica: Any further questions?
Jason: Nopez
Player: That's all I got
Nina: Great, can I go now?
Jessica: You're all dismissed
Jessica: We'll start initiations on Monday
Jessica: So be ready for anything boys and sluts
=> END"
